message.body: So, I'm guessing it wasn't really up to me. Still wish you all the best, though.
ooh, sorry, i must've dismissed your last text on accident when the morning after.
Right. I can take the cue. I just wish you'd be straight with me.

*when i woke up the morning after. look, i'm not going to tell you that i do or do not want to talk to you. that's all there is. if you're getting impatient with me, then there shouldn't be reason for either of us to be put out.
Not getting impatient. And I'm sorry if I was rude. I'm just getting mixed messages and it's confusing as heck. I'm sorry.
well, i'm generally pretty confused anyway. so welcome to the party.
